## Docker Compose 编排

基础设施: `bubble-mysql`(33306), `bubble-redis`(36379), `bubble-register/Nacos`(8848/9848)
统一网络: `spring_cloud_default` (bridge)

## 模块间调用关系

```
Bubble-UI → Nginx → bubble-gateway:9999
                         ↓ (路由转发)
              ┌──────────┼──────────┐
              ↓          ↓          ↓
         bubble-auth  bubble-biz-*  bubble-visual-*
              ↓ (Feign)  ↓ (Feign)
         bubble-api-backend (RemoteUserService等)
```

配置中心: 所有服务 → Nacos (`optional:nacos:...` 方式)
